          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-[1.15] relative" data-ps="src/pages/industries/electronics.astro:hs97tp">
            Dans le domaine de l&#x27;électronique, la relation avec le produit <span class="italic font-serif text-blue-600" data-ps="src/pages/industries/electronics.astro:6lp6t9">se poursuit</span> bien au-delà de l&#x27;achat.
          </h2>
          <div class="mt-12 space-y-8" data-ps="src/pages/industries/electronics.astro:dz28d3">
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/industries/electronics.astro:mw4ua">
              TieBack
